{"tid":2320293,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[武肺] 出街摸過野 會唔會即刻酒精消毒？","createTime":"2020-12-10T16:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T03:03:34.000Z","uid":210755,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"273a1a6911659682cb03022b55fc188a4e20a6c4","tid":2320293,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"宜家出街都隨身袋樽仔消毒火酒 &amp; 酒精啫喱<br />\n開門, 用兩隻手指, 摸完會即刻消毒，搭巴士單手扶完 落車又狂搓手我， 總之一隻手摸過街外野 另一隻就幫佢消毒<br />\n有fd已經幾日無沖涼 話凍無出汗, 幾日換一隻口罩, 出街無帶酒精 扶手摸野後 照摸電話 一切如常，去完廁所 用水滴hi一hi濕兩節手指頭 之後用件衫抹乾當洗左<br />\n我算唔算恐懼撚？"},{"pid":"8956a5f5e85a6309c996950be11cffdd1272782b","tid":2320293,"uid":172192,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"你個FD唔係人類黎喎"},{"pid":"b0322ec90a3ad12409d652d7d61d54f32b8af46a","tid":2320293,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"恐懼到呢"},{"pid":"3c2252d6854a5aa8eb9fc542fe167194af96fedf","tid":2320293,"uid":316021,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b00e2ef7e101d9b70d4fc3d1820c2af95e7f6d4","tid":2320293,"uid":228143,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:38:32.000Z","msg":"如果我係肺炎一定搞你先<br />\n<br />\n見你行步路都驚 同撞鬼一樣<br />\n<br />\n你個fd信念夠呢d先唔易撞鬼"},{"pid":"f0c46319a9f5000151e69ff0e95b9fa912ccd5db","tid":2320293,"uid":65439,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:55:41.000Z","msg":"其實我武肺前已經係咁<br />\n因為見過d痴線佬摸完碌鳩之後渣扶手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自此就有d潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdcdb4ee7309319cc71200e18893c9e69f6c280","tid":2320293,"uid":316021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f0c46319a9f5000151e69ff0e95b9fa912ccd5db","tid":2320293,"uid":65439,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020